@LandoInvests No. Point was that it's not a good idea to sell high-beta like $RDDT or $SOFI after dropping 30-40% to reposition into crowded plays like defense/oil that have already been frontrun and are ATHs.   

For me personally with my oil/defense hedges, I'm looking for any major retail selloff to net reposition long in a lot of these names.   

I was just thinking institutions might do the same.

@AirExpel If you want to play semantics it’s not literally zero. But close to that. 

People don’t use $RDDT like Quora. 

